    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works or parts of works made from lead, particularly sculptural, ornamental, or architectural objects. Usage may include plumbing or glazier's work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
